## Frontmatter Requirements

### Evolution Posts

See `_data/config.yml → templates.evolution_post.frontmatter` for complete specification.

**Required fields:**
```yaml
layout: post
title: "Post Title"
date: YYYY-MM-DD
categories: [Category1, Category2]
tags: [tag1, tag2]
project: "{project-id}"
evolution_number: {N}
```

**Optional fields:**
```yaml
mermaid: true  # Default for evolution posts
evolution: "Evolution {N}: {Title}"
evolution_focus: "{Focus}"
```

### Generic Posts

